## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **AMD blindness 진정한 cure 없음** — anti-VEGF (wet AMD) 가 vision loss slowing; pegcetacoplan/avacincaptad (dry AMD 2023) 도 progression slowing only. quantum-VQE 의 새 mechanism (regenerative) 가 future direction.
2. **glaucoma irreversible** — IOP lowering 이 standard, 단 retinal ganglion cell death 자체는 stop 못함. neuroprotection / neurorestoration novel mechanism 필요.
3. **gene therapy paradigm (Luxturna 2017)** = first FDA gene therapy in any disease — VIROCAPSID axis 의 가장 명확 win.
4. **hearing loss drug 부재** — FX-322 등 research 단계, 진정한 disease-modifying 약 없음.
5. **optogenetics paradigm** — GS030 phase 1/2 시각 부분 회복 (Cell 2021); novel modality + non-pharmacological.
6. **post-COVID anosmia** = ~5-10% long COVID; mechanism 불명확. quantum 직접 X.
7. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, sensory 임상 의미 한정.

